				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">One caution: If you're using only $2000 and $2005 for horizontal scroll splits, you need to write a value consisting of the coarse scroll ($2000 bit 0 and $2005.1st bits 7-3) for the <em>next</em> line combined with the fine scroll ($2005.1st bit 2-0) for the <em>current</em> line. <em>Super Mario Bros.</em> leaves line 31 blank (and Vs. SMB and SMB2J squish the numbers in the font) because this wasn't completely figured out in 1985. It might be conceptually simpler to just use <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/viewtopic.php?p=105762#p105762" class="postlink">tokumaru's $2006-$2005-$2005-$2006 snippet</a> throughout.</div>

