						<div class="postbody">It doesn't matter what register you're using, as long as your interrupt saves/restores any registers it uses (normally all three unless you have a special reason not to).<br /><br />Also, NMI or IRQ does not need to PHP/PLP. This is implicit in the interrupt and RTI.</div>

